TopicTitle: My headcanon for the matt lowne no timewarp mission!

Articles.Content: Lowne Aerospace has lost all of their krakenite and can no longer timewarp! With this new development the kerbals are very scared about the effects of longterm spaceflight! The test mission they have launched is heading to the mun, for the kerbals do not wish to do a 4 year long mission to jool. what can be learned about kerbal anatomy from this mission? Will Jeb survive? What happened to the snacks in the mobile processing lab?  Nobody knows!!!!!!!!
